Music is a big inspiration for me in my work and being able to translate how certain songs make me feel.. I dedicate this to Utada Hikaru, an artist who will forever be apart of my life. I highlighted the years of her 7 Japanese albums which is also the number of editions this will have. This is a one of a kind that embodies my style and this amazing artist who has a timeless effect on our ears and emotions through her lyrics and singing
